Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,NICE\N(SOUTHERN FRANCE)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara, how about a Moscow mule?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thank you, Michael.\N-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz, I have some juice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz, say "Thank you" to your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is what it is.\NHe'll get used to me with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The new antique artwork business I started\Nwill take time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-But it's very sudden to me.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I suddenly get to live in\Nsuch a wonderful house
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and have such a kind husband\Nwho makes delicious cocktails for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you sense something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,From the house next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It sometimes feels like someone\Nis watching from the second floor window.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.98,0:01:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. Isn't that house empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I heard something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,from Daughtry across the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that house, 20 years ago,\Na married couple was slaughtered
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and a ghost has been appearing\Nin that house since.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong, Michael?\N-Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you believe\Nsuch stories too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of sometimes having\Noutings with just the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we won't need a bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that should help Fritz\Nwarm up to you faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what I'm going for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best as Fritz's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective, what did you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The police are chasing him, as he is\Na suspect in the Fortner couple murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,However, his whereabouts are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is what Tenma said\Nwhen he was summoned by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy whose life he saved ten years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,killed the director and two doctors\Nat the Eisler Memorial Hospital and fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy's name is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He says Johan later showed himself again\Nafter becoming an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and committed another murder\Nin front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Nina Fortner,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the daughter of the murdered couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She also remains unaccounted for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Messener.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I traced his route and went to Frankfurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-What?\N-About two months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he was stabbed repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he was dragged into\Nsome drug-related troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Messener was my partner\Nduring my days as a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Messener got involved with drugs\Nand was dismissed from the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:05:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who saved him\Nwas a man called the Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Baby acts as the face\Nof a far-right organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This past winter in Frankfurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,there was an arson incident\Nin the Turkish Village, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that the Baby\Nwas the mastermind behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And during this incident, an Asian man\Nput out the fires and stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That Asian man's name is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If that man is Dr. Tenma…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it is said that the Baby\Ncaused the arson incident
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,as a ritual to welcome a young man\Nwho would be their organization's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the name of the boy Dr. Tenma\Nsaved through surgery ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man that the Baby's organization\Ntried to worship as their leader
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is also named Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your move, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My life is like\Nthis chess piece, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, until I received\Nthat single phone call,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,my life was a complete failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a detective\Nalong with my partner, Messener,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we got involved in illegally selling\Nconfiscated drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The caller knew everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.03,0:07:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me to kill a certain couple\Nif I wanted him to keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fortner couple in Heidelberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be spared if we killed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, there was one more person\Nwho was a newspaper reporter or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Messener and I killed all three of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After that,\Na large sum of money was wired to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was picked up by the syndicate\Nafter I quit the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And they suddenly put me in a nice post.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I easily laundered the money I earned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you met your current wife\Nand went straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I leave\Nthe organization so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the person that called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who wired me all that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who is controlling my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, I give you my thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for always protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then can you hold off\Non that move just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one request I can't fulfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.77,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off then, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, stay safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, buy me a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to\Nsay goodbye to your dad, Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All he can think about is toys right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, any contact from the detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto,\Nsomething happened to the detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, come here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The daughter of\Nthe Fortner couple you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do this? Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who killed him\Nwas your bodyguard, Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it all from the house next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto is a trusted friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here to get revenge on me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking this bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay here if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's if there's anyone\Nyou can even trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Mr. Müller?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Müller?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been watching me\Nfrom next door all this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So much I want to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was threatened into doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I didn't kill your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,he said he'd expose\Nthat I was illegally selling drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I had no choice\Nbut to do it with Messener.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You had no choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They were wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother and father\Nloved me from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I wasn't their real daughter,\Nmy mother and father…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.18,0:12:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They truly…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet they were killed by trash like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is what it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time\NFritz, that boy, called me Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.42,0:13:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I now have something I don't want to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was that café in Düsseldorf,\Nevery morning at eight o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My boss gave me an order\Nwhen I joined the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feigned an orderly life every morning,\Nas if I were a salaryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning,\Na mother passed by with her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it was just a single point\Nthat connected me with a respectable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you ask\Nthat detective to investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The whereabouts of you and Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the movements of Messener,\Nmy partner from when I was in the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But Messener is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked him to do a detailed\Nfollow-up investigation on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The detective called me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have gotten quite strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.53,0:15:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Messener was already a junkie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and was not involved in\Ntrouble with the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the culprit was not involved\Nwith the organization in Frankfurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but the Düsseldorf…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Düsseldorf?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.67,0:15:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll share more details\Nwhen we meet next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A draft of the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"Culprit of the Messener Incident."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who is Roberto?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like the bag back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife and Fritz\Nare relaxing next to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let my family go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You should hurry back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to your wonderful family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-A gun.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I borrow a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That gun only works at point-blank range
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and it only has four bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a former police detective, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.49,0:16:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Since if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell the cops\Nthe truth for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you absolutely can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll support you from next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, look! It's a fishing rod!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He was so insistent,\Nsaying he wants you to take him fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Barbara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend from his security firm\Nis here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened while we were away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently there was no damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Roberto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.09,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the glass windows was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be a prank by a local kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the investigator's corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto, who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife and Fritz might see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, calm down. Come now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, we'll make it\Nas if nothing happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was another peaceful day
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and these days will continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful girl she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving her a hospitable welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She is an important guest\Nto a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy's name is Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan this and Johan that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is this Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to live happily\Nwith your wife and Fritz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That is good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for our long time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I bid you farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do with Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.87,0:19:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, when will you take me fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, if it's sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't see the ghost anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have such nice eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You look much like Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When can I meet Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came obediently\Nbecause you said I could meet Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to meet you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.13,0:20:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He is living happily in Munich.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is truly unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, next is…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a former police detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll reach your house soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised Fritz\NI'd take him fishing tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be sunny.
